list.abstract: 《Delicate》是由美国流行女歌手泰勒·斯威夫特录唱的一首流行歌曲，该歌曲被收录在歌手的第六张录音室专辑《reputation》。
Damien Rice 来自爱尔兰，出生于七十年代早期，绘画与写歌是他青年时期的兴趣，也因此让他有了组团的念头，在"O"的专辑内页有些插画便是 Damien Rice 自己的作品。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything you see exists together in a delicate balance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世界上所有的生命，都有他存在的价值。

yingyinNormal.en: You should know that my son has extremely delicate digestion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道我儿子消化不良。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a nice teapot, Mr. Bull. Yes Peppa, it's made of delicate china. Mr. Bull likes delicate china.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个漂亮的茶杯，公牛先生。是的，佩奇，这是由精美的瓷器做成的。公牛先生喜欢精美的瓷器。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a nice teapot, Mr. Bull. Yes Peppa, it's made of delicate china. Mr. Bull likes delicate china.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一个漂亮的茶杯，公牛先生。是的，佩奇，这是由精美的瓷器做成的。公牛先生喜欢精美的瓷器。

yingyinNormal.en: This is why he liked Yao Niang. Her feet were small, delicate, perfect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以他才喜欢窅娘，就因为她的脚小巧精致，堪称完美。

yingyinNormal.en: No, look, it's really good, actually. I mean, it's fragile. It's it's delicate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，那部剧真的很棒。我是说，很精致。微妙而细致。

yingyinNormal.en: Easy, easy, Lily. Forget everything you've ever heard about eggs. They're actually quite delicate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别激动，莉莉，忘记掉你听过的一切关于蛋的传闻，它们其实很易碎。

yingyinNormal.en: Wolowitz, you will be completing a series of delicate surgical procedures on the classic children's game Operation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 沃罗威茨，你要在经典儿童游戏"手术"上面完成一系列精细外科手术。

yingyinNormal.en: It's that first moment when you hold your baby girl and you didn't know that anything could be so small or so delicate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你第一次捧着小婴儿，想不到它会如此的小小，娇弱。

yingyinNormal.en: Not really. Most people didn't get the point of him. He was so delicate. But he was as kind to me as any man has ever been.
yingyinNormal.zh: 并不是，很少有人理解他，他...很敏感，但他对我很好，别人比不上。

yingyinNormal.en: If you wake up one morning with 1,000 times the strength you had the night before, how will you handle delicate day-to-day tasks?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果某天早上你醒来发现你的力量是昨晚的一千倍，你该如何处理那些日常的精细活？

yingyinNormal.en: What is happening? I need your advice about a delicate workplace situation. To protect those involved, I'll be changing their names.
yingyinNormal.zh: 发生什么事了？我需要你们为一件敏感的职场关系给意见，为了保护当事人隐私，我会替他们取假名。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm in kind of in a delicate spot, stuck between my wife and the guy next door, but I'm pretty sure I can satisfy them both simultaneously.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在处境有点微妙，夹在老婆和隔壁的哥们之间左右为难，不过我有把握同时满足他们两个。

yingyinNormal.en: These are the kind of little delicate compliments which are always acceptable to the ladies, and which I conceive myself particularly bound to pay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样巧妙的恭维话一般都会让太太小姐们听得高兴，我总觉得我应该在这方面特别留意。

yingyinNormal.en: This is exactly what I'm talking about. What kind of a guy makes delicate French cookies? They're not even butch, manly cookies with you know, with chunks!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就正是我在说的什么样的男人会做精致的法式饼干呢？看起来根本不像是男性化 雄纠纠的饼干，有那种，你知道的，大块咬的快感！

yingyinNormal.en: And I use a fluffy blending brush first to apply it underneath the delicate parts of my skin, like underneath my eyes and also just the hard-to-get corners like in-between my nose and my mouth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我使用的是蓬松的眼影刷，将它涂抹在皮肤最脆弱的地方，像是眼睛的下方，还有鼻子和嘴的两侧。
